**Problem 52 (Implement the specific function)**

Purpose: function, z = (x^y) & x.

Source:https://hdlbits.01xz.net/wiki/Mt2015_q4a

Exercise:
module top_module (input x, input y, output z);

    assign z=(x^y)&x;
endmodule


**Problem 53 (Implement the specific function, using K-map to optimize the circuit)**

Purpose: Implemetn the specific funciton.

Source:https://hdlbits.01xz.net/wiki/Mt2015_q4b

Exercise:
module top_module ( input x, input y, output z );
    assign z=(!x&!y)+(x&y);
endmodule

